'''Tish Pahl''' co-authored three short stories with [[Chris Cassidy]], which featured the female protagonists [[Fenig Nabon]] and [[Ghitsa Dogder]]. Two of the stories, "[[Hutt and Seek]]" and "[[Simple Tricks]]," appeared in the anthology ''[[Tales from the New Republic]]''.

